# Employee Management System

A Java-based Employee Management System using JDBC and MySQL.

## Features

- Add Employee
- Update Employee
- Delete Employee
- View Employee
- MySQL Database Integration
- JDBC Connectivity

## Technologies Used

- Java
- OOP
- JDBC
- MySQL
- IntelliJ IDEA

## Project Structure

```
src
├── model
│   └── Employee.java
├── dao
│   └── EmployeeDAO.java
├── util
│   └── DBConnection.java
└── Main.java
```

## Database

Database Name:

```
employee_db
```

Table:

```sql
CREATE TABLE employees(
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100),
    department VARCHAR(100),
    salary DOUBLE
);
```

